<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				background-color: #f9f9f9;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
			}
			.container {
				background-color: #ffffff;
				border-radius: 8px;
				padding: 20px;
				box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);

				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			h1 {
				color: #e63946;
			}
			p {
				color: #333;
				line-height: 1.5;
			}
			.qr-code {
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 10px 20px;
				background-color: #dc143c;
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				border-radius: 5px;
				transition: background-color 0.3s;
			}
			.button:hover {
				background-color: #d62839;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<img
				width="200px"
				height="200px"
				src="../../../../../../../public/logo.png"
				alt="Love loom logo"
			/>

			<h1>Your Looveloom was created!</h1>

			<p>Dear {{user}},</p>

			<p>
				We’re thrilled to help you celebrate your love story. Your page
				has been successfully created - now share it with the world!
			</p>

			<h2>Access Your Love Story:</h2>
			<p>
				To view your personalized page, you can scan the QR code below
				or click the link below:
			</p>

			<div class="qr-code">
				<img src="{{qrcode}}" alt="Your QR Code" />
			</div>

			<strong>or</strong>

			<p>
				<a href="{{url}}" class="button">View Your Page</a>
			</p>

			<p>
				If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach
				out to our support team at support@looveloom.com. We’re here to
				help!
			</p>

			<p>
				Thank you for choosing LooveLoom. We hope you cherish every
				moment!
			</p>

			<p>
				Warm regards,
				<strong>The LooveLoom Team</strong>
			</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
